data.description: If you are looking for a home with a large detached shop area, take a closer look, because this may be the one you have been waiting for.  This home has been meticulously cared for inside and out and with the fresh coat of paint it shines like new.  The cozy living room feels warm and inviting and flows seamlessly into the dining room and kitchen area or down the hallway where you will find the bathroom and three decently sized bedrooms.  Just off the kitchen, you can either enter the attached one car garage, go downstairs into the partially finished basement, or go outside to the patio area.  The basement has a dry bar and plenty of space for an additional living area as well as an office area and a bonus room!  Stepping outside and following the concrete walkway to the back of the house, you will find a secluded patio area for entertaining family and friends.  The heated and cooled, detached two car garage / shop area (measuring in at 31'x23') is a worker’s dream and truly a must see!  The heater can be purchased separately.  **The property has a new roof as of 2022 which has a transferable warranty to the new owner, giving you coverage for the next 10 years and a Home Warranty!**  Don't let this one pass you by.  Schedule your private showing today.
